    {
      "type": "fill_in_the_blank",
      "question": "假设图中M=1，Diff模块输出\\(\\Delta V_p[n]=V_p[n]-V_p[n-1]\\)，且Acc.模块输出的估计系数\\(\\alpha=\\hat{\\Delta t}/T\\)为常数，则该插值器的Z域传递函数\\(H(z)=\\dfrac{V_{int}(z)}{V_p(z)}=\\underline{\\quad}\\).(选项如下：1,alpha*z^{-1}+(1-alpha), 5, 1+alpha(1-z^{-1}))",
